PIG has two types of data types

Simple and Complex

Simple:
=======
int
long
float
double
chararray
bytearray
boolean
datetime

Complex:
========

tuple: An ordered set of fields. ex: (15,2)
bag: A collection of tuples. ex: {(15,2), (18,4)}
map: A set of key value pairs. Ex: [ key#value <, key#value â€¦> ]
